    {
      "id": "39",
      "name": "推薦角色",
      "components": [
        {
          "component_id": "customize",
          "data": {
            "data": {
              "parsed_content": [
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "amount": 1,
                      "display_style": "card",
                      "ep_id": 19,
                      "icon_url": "https://bbs.hoyolab.com/hoyowiki/picture/character/Traveler_icon.png",
                      "menu_id": 2,
                      "name": "旅行者（風）",
                      "type": "custom_entry"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "color:#ffffff"
                      ],
                      "text": "風元素主角長按元素戰技的風渦劍可以進行元素轉化並不斷發生擴散反應，該武器副詞綴的",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "bold",
                        "color:#ffe14b"
                      ],
                      "text": "元素精通",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "color:#ffffff"
                      ],
                      "text": "可以增加擴散反應的傷害，同時長按元素戰技以達到最大爆風所需時間超過2秒，在這期間內切割傷害和額外附帶的元素傷害能夠將該武器的特效提高至最大層數，使爆風傷害最大化。",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "amount": 1,
                      "display_style": "card",
                      "ep_id": 22,
                      "icon_url": "https://bbs.hoyolab.com/hoyowiki/picture/character/Kaedehara Kazuha_icon.png",
                      "menu_id": 2,
                      "name": "楓原萬葉",
                      "type": "custom_entry"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "color:#ffffff"
                      ],
                      "text": "萬葉的固有天賦【風物之詩詠】能夠以自身",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "bold",
                        "color:#ffe14b"
                      ],
                      "text": "元素精通",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "color:#ffffff"
                      ],
                      "text": "為基礎提供全隊的對應元素增傷。該武器副詞條能為萬葉提供較高的精通數值，可以有效地觸發萬葉固有天賦的增益效果。該武器為鍛造武器，獲得方式簡單，沒有精煉的需求，是平民玩家最好的選擇之一。",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                }
              ]
            }
          }
        }
      ]
    }
